about.description: 'A inspector widget to view and modify style sheet of a Qt app in runtime.'
about.summary: A inspector widget to view and modify style sheet of a Qt app in runtime.

name: qt_style_sheet_inspector
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "qt_style_sheet_inspector" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "76d019764bc1ca988a0dfec59f4fad9a7ea7c8122f9549e3650e954aa9d3262e" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed
  
requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  requires:
    - pyqt
  imports:
    - qt_style_sheet_inspector


about:
  home: https://github.com/ESSS/qt_style_sheet_inspector
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'A inspector widget to view and modify style sheet of a Qt app in runtime.'
  description: |
    'A inspector widget to view and modify style sheet of a Qt app in runtime.'
  dev_url: https://github.com/ESSS/qt_style_sheet_inspector

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - williamjamir
    - nicoddemus
